File: src/auth/login.js
Line: 14
Severity: Critical
Issue: `pool.query()` is awaited inside an async function with no try/catch — a DB error will produce an unhandled promise rejection and crash the request.
Fix: Wrap the query (and the rest of the handler body) in a try/catch that returns a 500 response on error.

