File: src/auth/login.js
Line: 22
Severity: Critical
Issue: Password is compared in plaintext against the stored value — bcrypt.compare() is never called, so hashed passwords will never match and unhashed passwords are a security breach.
Fix: `const match = await bcrypt.compare(password, user.password); if (!match) { return res.status(401)... }`

