Issue: `requireAdmin` is defined but never registered before admin routes in the router — admin-only endpoints are unprotected regardless of the caller's role.
Fix: Explicitly apply `requireAdmin` as middleware on every admin route, e.g. `router.delete('/users/:id', authMiddleware, requireAdmin, deleteUser)`.
